name: Nils Axel Gustafsson Bennich
obverse: Bust of Nils Axel Gustafsson Bennich facing left.
reverse: A cornucopia and caduceus crossed. Behind them is a branch.
references: Kungl. Vitterhets, Historie Och Antikvitets Akademiens Handlingar, Volumes 30-33, 1889 #5
description: Nils Axel Gustafsson Bennich was appointed director of the Swedish Customs Service.
